content.rendered:
Directed by Vikram Sirikonda.

Written by A. Deepakraj. Vikram Sirikonda. Sreenu Bosani. Ravi Reddy Mallu.

Cast Ravi Teja(Karthikeya). Raashi Khanna(Pushpa). Seerat Kapoor(Divya). Murli Sharma(Commissioner). V. Jayaprakash(Karthikeya’s father). Sayaji Shinde(DGP Ramachandra). Vennela Kishore(Balaram). Ajay(Police Officer). Satyam Rajesh(Rajesh). Vajja Venkata Giridhar(Mallesh Yadav). Satya(Anand Goud). Shritej(Sathyadev). Shahbaaz Khan(Rauf Lala). Freddy Daruwala(Irfan Lala). Jeeva(Moula). Vijayakumar(Chief Minister (as Vijay Kumar)). Aadukalam Naren(CI Murugesan). Vineet Kumar(Keshava Prasad). Muthu Kumar(Selvam).Prabhu.Madhav Rao. Gundu Sudharshan(Sudarshan).Ananth. Duvvasi Mohan(Constable Perumal). Sammeta Gandhi(Swamy). Anchor Ravi(Sandeep). Kireeti(Dheeraj). Darbha Appaji Ambarisha(Muslim MLA contestant). Getup Srinu(Wasim).Charandeep Surneni. Santosh Kumar Yadav(Antagonist (as Santhosh Yadav)). Surya Rao(Inspector Rishi).Lakshman.Govind Rao.Rasheed.Srinivas Yadav.Lab Sharath.Koteshwar Rao.Vajpai.Venkatesh Goud.Ramesh Naidu.Mahendranath.Subhash.Captain Chowdary.Sridhar Naana.Tharuni. Pooja Jhaveri(Sandhya).Suhasini. Sriranjani(Karthikeya’s mother). Annapoorna(Karthikeya’s grandmother). Kaumudi(Shalini). Aaradhya(Aaradhya) .Feroz Abbasi.Anjali.Chaitanya.Choudari.Geethanjali.Sandhya Janak.Kiriti.Vinith Kumar.Mrudula. K Muthukumar((as Muthukumar)).Lakshmi Narayana.Anitha Nath.Naveena.Rajitha.Usha Rani.Jayaprakash Reddy.Rohini.Shekar.Tej Shri.Sirisha.Soujanya.Srinivas.Vajpei.Isheeka Varma.Fish Venkat

Language Telugu.

Producers Vallabhaneni Vamsi Mohan. Nallamalupu Sreenivas.

Production Sri Lakshmi Narasimha Productions. Goldmines Telefilms.
